            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-01-05T21:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-05-31T23:30:00-05:00" n="1098" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d1098">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The question of establishing an American Consulate at Kuwait was discussed on
                    November 22 by Department officers with Michael Wright, Superintending Under
                    Secretary of State in the British Foreign Office. For the statement agreed to by
                    the United States and United Kingdom Groups, see <ref target="#pg_85">page
                        85</ref>.</p>
            </div>
